      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description" typeId="0207-88db-7926-4ba6">The model gains Deadly(5+) on one of its weapons. If the weapon already has the rule, increase Deadly(x+) by 1. For example Deadly(5+) becomes Deadly(4+).</characteristic>
